--JoeThe design inference reached based on our knowledge of what nature, operating freely can & cannot do, coupled with our knowledge of what designing agencies can do.---We do not know that designing agencies can design a genome or a flagella. There is no inference to best explanation.The design infernence is alo not disallowed, it's just that it cannot compete with the 'we don't know' explanation as it fails to add anything.SImple really